name: PRE-WEDDING EVENTS
description: Pre-wedding are a big part of your cultural wedding story. The colorful and classical photos from these events increase the amount of photos you will receive as part of your wedding package.

name: ENGAGEMENT SESSION
description: An engagement session is a fun and creative 3 hour photo shoot done prior to your wedding. It allows you to become comfortable with me as your photographer and me to get to know you better as a couple. You will have 50 edited photos to use for invitations and/or to display at your wedding.

name: WEDDING ALBUM
description: A stunning leather flush mount album is the final masterpiece of your beautiful wedding. When browsing through the 30 pages of your individually designed 10” x 10” photo album, you and your friends can relive the story of your wedding day.
